Unfortunately your code is not so clear. Do you mean that key or value of your map is `String`? Let&#39;s assume that key is string and value can be either string or map. (BTW this extremely bad practice, so I&#39;d recommend you to ask other question where you describe what your task is and ask how to design your program.)


