First of all, any code with sufficient permission of invoking the `System#setProperty(String, String)` subroutine can modify the returned literal at will. However, that&#39;s not necessarily the primary issue here, as it can be resolved through the use of a so called `SecurityManager`, as described in greater detail over [here][1].

